==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Spicewood
<hw>Spice"wood`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Bot.)</fld>
<def>An American shrub (<spn>Lindera Benzoin</spn>), the bark of which
has a spicy taste and odor; -- called also <altname>Benjamin</altname>,
<altname>wild allspice</altname>, and <altname>fever
bush</altname>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Spiciferous</ent>⟦br⟧
